# 🛠️ Setup Instructions

This guide explains how to clone, configure, and run the AldoReyes84.github.io portfolio locally.

---

## 📦 Requirements

To preview or contribute to this project, make sure you have:

- Git
- Jekyll (Ruby-based static site generator)
- Node.js (optional, for asset bundling or NPM packages)
- A modern browser (Chrome, Edge, Firefox)

---

## 📥 Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/AldoReyes84/AldoReyes.github.io.git
cd AldoReyes.github.io



🧱 Folder Structure Overview
├── _includes/          # Reusable HTML fragments (header, nav, panels)
├── _layouts/           # Base layout templates
├── assets/             # CSS, JS, images, icons
├── docs/               # Documentation files
├── index.md            # Main landing page
├── _config.yml         # Global configuration variables



⚙️ Configuration
Edit _config.yml to customize:
- title, description, url, baseurl
- Theme colors and font family
- Navigation labels and social links
These variables are injected into layouts and includes using Liquid syntax:
{{ site.title }}
{{ site.nav.home }}
{{ site.theme_color }}



🚀 Run locally with Jekyll
If you're using Bundler:
bundle install
bundle exec jekyll serve


Then open http://localhost:4000 in your browser.

🧪 Development Tips
- Use the dev branch for layout and visual testing
- Modularize components in _includes/
- Track changes in docs/changelog.md
- Use semantic HTML and accessibility attributes (aria-label, role, tabindex)

📤 Deployment
To publish the site:
- Enable GitHub Pages in repository settings
- Set source to main branch and root folder
- Push changes to main to trigger deployment

🧩 Related Repositories
This portfolio links to multiple thematic sections:
- Contoso Sales Dashboard
- AdventureWorks2022 Analysis
- SSIS Integration with Python Faker
Each section shares the same layout and navigation logic.

🧠 Notes
- All dropdown panels and navigation elements are modular
- Layout is responsive and optimized for desktop and mobile
- Future enhancements include bilingual support and internal search
